└── NFS

1.Empty Dir:

this is depandent on pod lifecycle, that is when pod is created ,volume gets created and when you delet the pod the volume and the content inside it aslo get deleted , 

syntex :
create the pod with volume and voulume mount 


apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: empty-directory
  namespace: default

spec:
  containers:
    - name: nginx
      image: nginx
      ports:
        - containerPort: 80
      volumeMounts:
        - name: empty-directory-volume
          mountPath: /data

  volumes:
    - name: empty-directory-volume
      emptyDir: {}

