DYNAMIC PROVISIONING:

	Generally here admin will not be creating the PV , insted the developer will create the PVC and this PVC will be approching the STORAGE CLASS for the required amount o vloume and storage class will crete the PV autometically and that will bound to PVC and that PVC will be mounted to the POD.


Eg: suppose there are 500 developer and each one need volume, and admin can not cret the PV for each induiadule each time as we did in "ststic provisioning" , insted we use "storage class" for it .

STORAGE CLASS: IT IS TEMPLATE WHICH WILL TELL THE KUBERNETES TO  CREAT THE STORAGE AUTOMETICALLY ,WHNE EVER THE DEVELOPER REQUET FOR STORAE





